  uniprot:* on measurement terms (xrefs). It does NOT capture UniProt IDs     
  reachable through the is_about (IAO_0000136) relationship to PR_ protein    
  terms. There are 6 additional measurement terms that would be captured      
  through the is_about path.                                                  
                                                                              
